{"tid":991266,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西伯利亞5歲小女孩為送媽媽驚喜 零下45℃步行30分鐘提早回家","createTime":"2019-01-22T09:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T11:24:00.000Z","uid":72009,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ceba053b255fe09b42f732ff34e78c174dfda225","tid":991266,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:02:30.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯西伯利亞雅庫特地區（Yakutia）是有人居住的全球最冷地區，當地有小女孩想給媽媽驚喜，相約偷偷溜出幼稚園，想在零下45℃嚴寒天氣下步行30分鐘提早回家，結果因凍傷並得了低溫症，要在醫院與媽媽見面。 <br />\n<br />\n兩個5歲小女孩為送媽媽驚喜，相約在正常接送時間前「偷走」。幼稚園的閉路電視拍到門口沒有職員看管，女童輕易打開大門離開，也沒有老師發現事件通知家長。 <br />\n<br />\n小女孩雖然有穿上厚厚衣物和冷帽，不過並不足以應付零下45℃的嚴寒，而且她們連手套也沒戴上。女童離園後各自回家，其中一位名為莉娜（Lena）的女孩在低溫之下極不適，向路過的一間民居敲門求救，她3隻手指凍傷。莉娜的朋友則因迷路，在一個小時後才被尋回。 <br />\n<br />\n莉娜的媽媽對傳媒表示︰「女兒大哭，兩個小孩都受驚了。」她在下午5時到幼稚園接女兒時發現她失蹤，「我們都嚇壞了，然後祖父來電說莉娜剛剛一個人回到家，淚流滿面、凍僵了。」 <br />\n<br />\n當局正調查為何2名女孩可以獨自離開幼稚園而不被發現，而且途上竟無人協助將她們帶回家，只有一人曾幫她們繫好頸巾。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190122/59169833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F59169833&d=4cMhME4%2F8xdsHij0ahPe44M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=8b49d456\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F59169833&h=a9dd6e20\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190122/59169833</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7a4f06d2a760965a4c7c2adb2732ebaf9a63c3","tid":991266,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80bf3b72cbb7d2f59996aa4ac23087fac94781b","tid":991266,"uid":37661,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190122/large/1548125258_79a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190122%2Flarge%2F1548125258_79a5.jpg&h=5cdee2ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n着得仲少過今日返工啲香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f199e44e2e7ec58329a80948fec25de3a11cd660","tid":991266,"uid":195588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:18:54.000Z","msg":"西伯利亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e769727ec989fd0d81231956c1a0ba43fbe3ae2d","tid":991266,"uid":106030,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:19:55.000Z","msg":"冬天的冠軍"},{"pid":"b3959335fa3b11f95d4251d1fd157004f45b6bf9","tid":991266,"uid":191926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"5歲 西伯利亞人 45度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439d7f9e5ea50f461b8354f1be17184d289e0ed8","tid":991266,"uid":46587,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:33:01.000Z","msg":"香港濕凍&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;西伯利亞負唔知幾多度"},{"pid":"a774ec5388a2f1dff906d57dad8033b7384fc8d5","tid":991266,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:33:20.000Z","msg":"賣火柴的小女孩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7707ec22b721bfee08b70045f040a4cd11ae3836","tid":991266,"uid":162075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:35:12.000Z","msg":"寒冬 跟我沒可能合襯"},{"pid":"512ed264601b4f510033bbf2c4c4f69691